rapy, or prophylactic vaccine; to introduce diagnostic ELISA testing. Clinical and epidemiological studies must be performed to describe viral dynamics and expansion of the outbreak.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Heukelbach, Jorg", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Alencar, Carlos Henrique", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kelvin, Alyson Ann", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Oliveira, Wanderson Kleber de", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Cavalcanti, Luciano Pamplona de G\u00f3es", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Chapter 4", "biodiversity", "environment assessment", "IPBES", "Alien Invasive Species Assessment AIS", "invasive species"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/05d50ee6f5f7b321fc6f4f6cdd6a0ef9", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/95d014f891ab5667f1593929cc01a87cb6fff92f5091af4e5e641896a25d3fb1", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/2352922/items/M9F9R6PS", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/2352922/items/M9F9R6PS", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/db85dd8d245a2aa8536b1b4d5e4ba473!/b65175-67283", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/359bd494433933b868f85e88d3437f76", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.3855/jidc.8217", "relation": "isVariantFormOf", "resource_type": "publication", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.7430682", "relation": "isCitedBy", "resource_type": "publication-report", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "02", "pages": "116-120", "title": "The Journal of Infection in Developing Countries", "volume": "10"}, "alternat